# Workspace sandbox scopes

When `git branch --show-current` matches `workspace/*`:

1. Read [.cursor/workspace-scopes/](../workspace-scopes/) for the active branch
2. Follow the matching scope skill (`widget-g7-*-scope`)
3. **Refuse** edits outside allowed paths — route fixes to the owning sandbox or `feat/bloc-*` on `integrate`
4. Before commit: `widget-g7-repo-hygiene` (no secrets, no `local.properties`, no real glucose in docs/qa)
5. PR to `integrate`: CI green + `widget-g7-pr-gatekeeper`

Pre v0.5.0 tag: only **`workspace/qa-hardware`** should have active code/evidence work; other sandboxes are dormant.

Post v0.5.0 tag: **`workspace/mobile-app`** is the primary active sandbox (Bloc F).

See [docs/plan/WORKSPACE.md](../../docs/plan/WORKSPACE.md).
